Open Jenkins Dashboard

Click New Item

Enter project name

Select Freestyle project → OK

Go to Source Code Management → Select Git

Enter repository URL

Under Build Environment, choose the correct JDK

Go to Build → Add build step

Select Invoke top-level Maven targets

In Goals, enter:

clean test install


(Optional) Add test reports:
Post-build Actions → Publish JUnit test result report

**/target/surefire-reports/*.xml


Click Save

Click Build Now
